@host=http://localhost:4004/odata/v4

### IT Department Employees
GET {{host}}/Employee/Employees?$filter=department eq 'd0011111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111'

### HR Department Employees
GET {{host}}/Employee/Employees?$filter=department eq 'd0022222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222'

### Finance Department Employees
GET {{host}}/Employee/Employees?$filter=department eq 'd0033333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333'

### IT Engineers
GET {{host}}/Employee/Employees?$filter=department eq 'd0011111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111' and designation eq 'ENGINEER'

### IT Employees Above 900000 Salary
GET {{host}}/Employee/Employees?$filter=department eq 'd0011111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111' and salary gt 900000

### Employees In HR Managed By Priya
GET {{host}}/Employee/Employees?$filter=department eq 'd0022222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222' and managerId eq 'e0022222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222'